flowchart TD
    A[Record has privacy level] --> B{Viewer state}

    B -->|Guest| C{Privacy}
    C -->|public| D[Allow show/index]
    C -->|community| E[Deny]
    C -->|private| E

    B -->|Signed-in person| F{Privacy}
    F -->|public| G[Allow show/index]
    F -->|community| H{Record resolves a community the viewer belongs to?}
    F -->|private| I{Existing special access?}

    H -->|yes| G
    H -->|no| E
    I -->|creator / manager / member / host / invite| J[Allow by policy-specific rule]
    I -->|no| E

    B -->|Manager / steward| K[Allow all privacy levels]

    D --> L[Rendered content and badges]
    G --> L
    J --> L
    K --> L
